E_D("replace into `hhs_goods` values('71','1','HHS000071','【测试商品-网站演示专用】先歇歇  芒果','+','150','0','','987','0.040','36.00','30.00','0.00','0','0','1','','卵圆形，果肉呈黄色，外层果肉甜，接近果核部分稍酸，风味独特。该品种具有纤维少，味甜芳香，营养丰富的优良品质，集热带水果精华于一身，素有热带果王的美誉。','<p style=\"color:#404040;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong>温馨提示：</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#404040;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	为了避免芒果运输途中损坏，我们都是采摘9成熟的发出的，您收到果果后一定要催熟后才能食用哦！\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#404040;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong>催熟方法：</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#404040;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	收到果果后把熟软的芒果挑出来，然后把生的原箱密封好，放在温度高点的地方2-5天可熟（每天都检查一下哦！）\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#404040;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong>禁忌：</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#404040;font-family:tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	由于芒果为热带后熟水果，没有催熟的芒果一定不能放冰箱。熟软后建议立即食用（可放冰箱暂存）\r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i4/2219843891/TB2_4_aepXXXXXRXXXXXXXXXXXX-2219843891.jpg\" style=\"border:0px;\" align=\"absmiddle\" /><img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i4/2219843891/TB2T_nbepXXXXXgXXXXXXXXXXXX-2219843891.jpg\" style=\"border:0px;\" align=\"absmiddle\" /><img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i2/2219843891/TB2UiC.epXXXXagXXXXXXXXXXXX-2219